[DESCRIPTION]
tjbench is a JPEG decompression/compression benchmark part of libjpeg-turbo.
It remains the authoritative committed input for the rendered staged tjbench(1)
page and documents the packaged benchmark surface, including -limitscans.
The staged Debian metadata installs the rendered page from safe/debian rather
than consulting ../original during package assembly.

[COMMENT]
This manual page was written by Mathieu Malaterre <malat@debian.org> for the
Debian GNU/Linux system, but may be used by others.

